<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mormon_folklore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Further reading"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFEliasonMould2013" class="citation book cs1">Eliason, Eric A.; Mould, Tom, eds. (2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://content.lib.utah.edu/cdm/singleitem/collection/upcat/id/1884/rec/1"><i>Latter-day Lore: Mormon Folklore Studies</i></a>. Salt Lake City: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Utah_Press" title="University of Utah Press">University of Utah Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-60781-284-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-60781-284-5"><bdi>978-1-60781-284-5</bdi></a>. <a href="/wiki/OCLC_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="OCLC (identifier)">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/854139803">854139803</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Latter-day+Lore%3A+Mormon+Folklore+Studies&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Utah+Press&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F854139803&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-60781-284-5&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontent.lib.utah.edu%2Fcdm%2Fsingleitem%2Fcollection%2Fupcat%2Fid%2F1884%2Frec%2F1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+folklore" class="Z3988"></span> A compilation of classic and contemporary essays in Mormon folklore studies.</li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWennergren2007" class="citation cs2">Wennergren, Mike (6 October 2007), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.deseretnews.com/article/695216121/Folklore-plays-role-for-LDS.html">"Folklore plays role for LDS: Professor says stories affirm values, beliefs"</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Deseret_News" title="Deseret News">Deseret News</a></i></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Deseret+News&amp;rft.atitle=Folklore+plays+role+for+LDS%3A+Professor+says+stories+affirm+values%2C+beliefs&amp;rft.date=2007-10-06&amp;rft.aulast=Wennergren&amp;rft.aufirst=Mike&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deseretnews.com%2Farticle%2F695216121%2FFolklore-plays-role-for-LDS.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+folklore" class="Z3988"></span> A news article summarizing William Wilson's ideas about the importance of Mormon folklore in Mormon culture.</li></ul>
