<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://lib.byu.edu/collections/wilson-folklore-archive/">William A. Wilson Folklore Archives</a> at <a href="/wiki/L._Tom_Perry_Special_Collections" class="mw-redirect" title="L. Tom Perry Special Collections">L. Tom Perry Special Collections</a>, <a href="/wiki/Harold_B._Lee_Library" title="Harold B. Lee Library">Harold B. Lee Library</a>, <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University" title="Brigham Young University">Brigham Young University</a>. Contains online summaries of student folklore research.</li>
